---
import Layout from "../layouts/layout.astro"
let no = ""
try {
	const response = await fetch("https://naas.isalman.dev/no")

	if (response.ok) {
		let data = await response.json()
		no = data.reason
	}
} catch {
}
---

<Layout>
	<div class="p-12 flex flex-col items-center gap-12">
	<p class="font-semibold text-3xl">Bienvenido!</p>
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 p-8 bg-gray-300 rounded-md">
		<p>Qué tipo de medida querés convertir?</p>
		<div class="flex gap-4 mt-4">
			<a href="/longitud" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-sky-600 text-white shadow-md hover:bg-sky-700">Longitud</a>
			<a href="/masa" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-sky-600 text-white shadow-md hover:bg-sky-700">Masa</a>
			<a href="/volumen" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-sky-600 text-white shadow-md hover:bg-sky-700">Volumen</a>
			<a href="/temperatura" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-md bg-sky-600 text-white shadow-md hover:bg-sky-700">Temperatura</a>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 p-8 bg-gray-300 rounded-md">
		<p>Manera ingeniosa de decir que no en inglés! <br> (Cortesía de No-as-a-Service)</p>
		<p class="italic">"{no}"</p>
	</div>
	</div>
</Layout>